Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:06.23,hinamatsuri_hm1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(884,542)}黑帮特别篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:06.23,hinamatsuri_hm1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(884,978)}当代黑帮现状
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.45,0:00:06.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有什么意见或建议吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:07.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,局长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:11.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想对一个男的进行跟踪采访
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:13.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:15.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是芦川组的新田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:17.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,本身是个智力派的黑帮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:22.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,却在之前的对抗中一个人端了敌对的筱冢全组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:24.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是个相当有传奇色彩的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:28.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,据说他们的正当收入还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:30.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这种有着昭和气息的黑帮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:33.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会吸引一波观众的眼球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:40.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 濑田
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:45.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于被任命为了负责人啊 一定要把它给干好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:47.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 一起上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:52.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 我濑田大介的取材开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:54.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然会是一次危险的取材
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:58.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但也会测试出我一个记者到底有多大实力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,纪录片取材
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:05.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要跟踪采访我？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:05.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:10.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是新田义史
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:15.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乍一看还是挺沉稳的 不知道他的内心究竟有多么残暴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:18.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 要是就拍我一个人就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:22.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然黑帮上的人不能用一般手段搞定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:26.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在黑帮业界 最势如破竹的就是新田先生你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.24,0:01:31.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让我为你拍摄你成为一代枭雄的序章吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:35.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要拍下真实的你 就必将成为传奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:42.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是把性命赌在了这上边 绝对不可以退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:47.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:50.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 关于这位实打实的武斗派
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:53.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田义史的跟踪采访开始了
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:59.30,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}どれだけ離れているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:06.40,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君の面影思い出す　ふとした時に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:27.48,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思い出の中　微笑んでるその横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:33.21,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}何気ない日々が　大切なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:38.01,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思う気持ち　それに今気付いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:40.82,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と笑って過ごした日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:43.63,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と言い合って泣いた日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:47.99,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と過ごした日々　愛しい日々
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.76,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}大切だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:56.19,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}ねえ　どれだけ離れているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:02.44,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君の温もり思い出しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:07.25,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遠くに見えるあの街の灯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:11.74,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君は笑えてるかな
Comment: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:59.30,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们究竟相距多远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:06.40,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}偶然一瞬 想起了你的容貌模样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:27.48,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}在记忆之中 你微笑着的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:33.21,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡无奇的日常 是无可替的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:38.01,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}这份思念之情 现在终于意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:40.82,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你欢笑度过的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:43.63,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你争论泪流的曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:47.99,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们携手的每一天 令人无比怜爱的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.76,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}十分珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:56.19,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们究竟相距多远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:02.44,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我又回忆起你的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:07.25,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遥遥可见的那条街道的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:11.74,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}你正展露着笑容吗
