Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:27.97,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\an8\c&HFFFFFF&}第十一话 渴求血与暴力与金钱的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:35.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在脚骨折了 顺便送她一程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接送
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:46.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 你是怎么成为黑帮的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:50.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大学时代本来想创办公司就去做了兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我兼职的地方就有黑帮背景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:56.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接触得多了 就觉得成为黑帮的话或许会赚得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是为了赚钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:02.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是为了赚钱 但钱也不是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也有一些人情世故在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:09.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲很早就去世了 我想帮家里做些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:11.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 是因为这种理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此啊 是为了你的家人或者女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是我女儿 我只是收养她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是被逼无奈 被逼无奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟没别人会养你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:26.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你跟女人的关系如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:29.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,听说黑帮在男女关系方面比较豪爽…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:31.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前确实是喜欢过一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她是那种把别人利用完就扔开的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:42.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那女儿你跟新田住在一起感觉如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他会给我做饭 新田是个大好人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这么让人难为情的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:52.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你被收养之前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总是被要求干这个干那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:04:59.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就是个好人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田的肉丸比我多一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:11.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来来轩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 秒杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是你太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:22.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错的 他肯定是对我们隐藏了本性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不肯轻易露出真面目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:30.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥的战斗史？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有没有 因为我哥是个乐于助人的好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:38.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗史的话还得说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 我还去抓过小混混来打呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:43.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正好当做空手道的练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还能练练危险动作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后最后被学校停课了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:54.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,采访新田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:57.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子 你还真是了不起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要给我组长添麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的计划正逐步偏离正轨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:06.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去看老爷子的慰问品买了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了 我现在马上去买
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 长点心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该发更大火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:22.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那家伙很笨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:24.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是整天都发火的话会很累的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:27.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:29.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底要隐藏本性到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:30.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:34.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全搞错了 黑帮要是这样的话会被观众看不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊大哥 动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:42.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我决不允许大哥被全国人民瞧不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:46.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来来来 用这个向全国观众证明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:48.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是有这个干劲的话 倒是用到工作上去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:51.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那咱们就从开头开始来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:54.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 1 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟班 去看老爷子的慰问品买了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,坏了 那个 我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就去买
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:07.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？你给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:11.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在耍我吗 你这个笨蛋呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:14.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且灰都洒出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是一直跟你说要好好打扫的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:21.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我马上打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:22.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拍了一段好东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:27.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你也砸得太狠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你们谁给我拿个医护包过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但这之后还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:35.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这就要回去了吗 晚上不去玩玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:37.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我得回家给雏做晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:39.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道是白…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是肠胃药啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:45.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 难道说他真的就是一个好人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:49.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,濑田 取材怎么样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:52.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,局长 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我拍到了相当劲爆的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一股黑帮仍未覆灭的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:01.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确是被逼到了绝境啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:14.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田先生 你说话跟举止就不能再浮夸点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说要拍真实的我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再说我就算是做了这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不就变成作假了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:25.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人就战胜一组人是真事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:27.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:32.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个老实记者都让你演戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我发飙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:37.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你喝醉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:41.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你 发 飙 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:42.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:50.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:54.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还觉得自己是记者 就别做这些无聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我们这些混黑帮的人不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,走在光明正道上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:01.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果连自己都看不清前方的路那怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:04.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:08.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就连你的说教都包括在内
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你实在是再普通不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:18.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能这么干了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能这么干了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:24.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是认真的吗 濑田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:27.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本就不是摆拍 而是捏造了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不配做一名记者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话 这也是没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:35.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有家人等着我养
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:38.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能失败啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 别打游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前来取材的节目今天要播放了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我事前确认的时候感觉不太有黑帮的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:48.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.23,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(864,452)}特集                                       当代黑帮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.23,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正姚体\pos(952,888)\c&H070707&}渴求血与暴力与金钱的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:12:38.94,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\blur2\3c&H28A994&\move(330,330,593.143,375.523,163024,166486)}{\move(354,394,591.143,409.523,163024,166695)}{\fs50\t(163024,166695,\fs30)\c&H030053&\3c&HFFFFFF&}特{\c&H171717&}集 当代黑帮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:12:38.94,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正姚体\fs50\blur2\move(354,394,595.143,419.523,163024,166695)}{\fs50\t(163024,166695,\fs30)\3c&HFFFFFF&}渴求{\c&H393CB7&\3c&HFFFFFF&}血{\c&H171717&}与暴力与金钱的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:55.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他坐在黑色高级轿车而来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:10:00.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,孤身一人闯进敌对势力的老巢 并将其一举歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:04.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是黑帮电影中极具传奇色彩的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他究竟是一个怎样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为了钱 钱就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:13.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,女人啊 吃完就扔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在耍我吗 你这个笨蛋呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:18.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:21.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钱 女人 以及暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:26.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个男人N 到底是经历过怎样的人生才会变成现在这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:30.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在N小的时候 父亲就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:32.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,从小便过着没人管的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:34.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他还去抓过小混混来打呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:36.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正好当做空手道的练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还能练练危险动作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:39.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最后被学校停课了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沉浸于打架乐趣中的N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最终没办法在家乡立足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:45.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,于是来到东京当起了黑帮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:50.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但就是这样的他 最初也只不过是想找一个立锥之地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:57.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(992,848)}{\bord3\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\c&H171717&\3c&HFFFFFF&}在黑帮老窝的对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:53.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他被组织当枪使
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:56.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他也就逐渐地不再相信别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:03.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1470,502)}{\frz270.3\pos(1460,516)\fn@微软雅黑}为什么组长对你会是这个态度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:03.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1490,174)}{\pos(1460,516)\fn@微软雅黑}Q
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:03.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1496,890)}{\pos(1460,516)\fn@微软雅黑}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那家伙很傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:08.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(520,0)\pos(1572,534)}{\frz270.3\pos(1460,516)\fn@微软雅黑}你们之间没有人情世故吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:08.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1594,248)}{\pos(1460,516)\fn@微软雅黑}Q
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:08.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1562,834)}{\frz270.3\pos(1460,516)\fn@微软雅黑}？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:07.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是做了这种事 不就变成作假了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:10.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,当他意识到之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经从昭和侠义黑帮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:16.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,变为了没有人情世故 称得上是「平成怪物」的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:21.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,从他的私人生活中也可以看出他缺少人情味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前和他玩过的女人生了个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但他却说这孩子是他收养的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:29.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们之前还对这个叫N的男人抱有一丝期待 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:30.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总是被要求干这个干那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:36.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘如此回答道 脚还是骨折的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像没有什么特别的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:41.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,N拒绝承认她是自己女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:43.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但她却说自己是他的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她的样子真的非常悲惨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:51.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对N来说 别人早就已经变成了他的敌人或者生财工具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:54.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最后我们采访了这样一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种活法 周围不就全是敌人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 秒杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:06.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后当所有采访结束 我们准备支付采访费用时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:07.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,N缓缓说道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:10.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你醉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:12.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对着吓了一跳的我们 N继续说道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:14.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别做这些无聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果连自己都看不清前方的路那怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:22.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在暗示我们 不再多给点钱的话就弄瞎我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:25.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在支付了10倍的金额后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,终于接受了的N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:30.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一边笑着 一边消失在夜里的街道中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:32.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经无法回头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:36.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个充斥着欲望的黑夜中不断前行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:39.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,直到毁灭为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:50.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那是什么鬼内容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:52.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 平成的怪物先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:55.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个笨蛋还真对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:56.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟老爹说了后他说要揍扁你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:01.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说「小雏不是你女儿到底是怎么一回事」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:05.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那全都是电视台自己动手捏造出来的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:07.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你醉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别做这些无聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经无法回头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:23.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个充斥着欲望的黑夜中不断前行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:26.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,直到毁灭为止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:29.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你把节目录下来背台词了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 那到底算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:36.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 雏 老是在玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作业做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 秒杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:45.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一股黑帮仍未覆灭的感觉
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始请多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:53.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏去了滑雪教室不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:04.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}生剥滑雪教室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:02.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还想着说正好碰上放假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:04.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是要看小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:05.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:10.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不跟中华店的大叔他们一起去温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:12.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔他们说难得去一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:14.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不想跟着去添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想让他们过过二人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:22.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给多少钱能把你跟雏交换啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:23.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:28.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我端出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:29.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,端菜我可熟得不了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:37.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,餐具收拾就让我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:41.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 你行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:42.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很擅长洗碗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明比想象中要轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,心里这股烦躁感到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是义史超加强版
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:12.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再多教我一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天休息 不出去外面玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:15.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:19.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想叔叔他们回来的时候能惊喜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:21.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是个好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:22.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}义史原创混合清洗剂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:26.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:31.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 好厉害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:34.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 才会进行比较
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,专业过头了反而有点恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,与雏真是云泥之别…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:58.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 有什么我能帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:00.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用这么勤奋也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子你是客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 毕竟我受你照顾着嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:04.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我会做我力所能及的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:09.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,互帮互助是很重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:22.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:26.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我好恨！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:28.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,中华店那群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:32.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我这边是雏 他们那边是杏子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么乖巧懂事的孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 怎么可能有这种孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:42.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最开始也不是现在这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:43.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,刚相遇的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:46.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是个更加依赖力量不讲理的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:49.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就让她回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 我们出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说要教我各种小技巧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:00.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,两三天的话绰绰有余啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:01.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:04.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的休息日 小孩子都会去玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我翻花绳很厉害哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:14.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会去玩那么蠢的游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂的话就跟着来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:20.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我会教你各种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最开始 雏和杏子并没有什么不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:28.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是环境让她们产生了区别
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让她记住跟雏一样的娱乐方式的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:35.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子也会回想起任性随意的孩子本性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,中华店的人也好好体会一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:39.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,养育孩子的幸苦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:40.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要花钱的话不来也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,切 净是谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:48.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 休息日就是奖励自己的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:54.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你叔叔他们也是为了能去旅行而赚钱的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:57.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看我不马上把你的好孩子面具扯下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去温泉也要花钱的呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:01.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:04.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要花钱的话 就能任意玩乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:21.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 慢一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:29.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好危险 突然就被治愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,浑身湿透啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要坚定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是演技
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:45.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是当流浪汉时为了生存下去而生出的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:51.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:55.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓小孩子 是更加忠于自己的欲求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:59.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,光会捣蛋给旁人添麻烦的生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:06.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 接下来去乘这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:08.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快一点快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:10.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:14.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为了对付这家伙的治愈攻击而制造出来的机会！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来很享受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:19.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 乘了这个后接下来就去新田想去的项目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:22.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 去杏子你喜欢的就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:27.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,平时不能提的任性要求今天都可以说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:28.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果休息日是愉快玩耍的日子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是两个人都乐在其中就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:41.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我比较想要跟新田一起开心享受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:42.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:43.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比较好……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:03.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:16.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没所谓了吧 就做个梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:20.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就做个梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:25.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做梦吧 做梦吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:45.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:48.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:51.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:06.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,当爸的想要的理想型女儿 就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:17.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是叔叔他们回来的日子 我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:20.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:22.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:24.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:30.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:33.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沉浸在理想型中 都要忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:36.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要回来了吗 现实！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:38.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你喊我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:43.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我是新田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:46.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是渡边中学的松谷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:48.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:53.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上现在举办中的滑雪教室…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:54.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:56.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然实在是难以辩解…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:02.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田雏在雪山里遇难了
